<div class="hero-unit">
    <h1>WebMap.Net!</h1>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>WebMap.Net is a .NET library designed to create content to be displayed using <a href="http://www.openlayers.org">OpenLayers</a>. The library is written in C#. </p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="/Examples/Index">Demo &raquo;</a></p>
